snippet.title: Leonel Gonçalves
snippet.description:
We are a channel mainly focused on comedy. Through our videos we will touch on subjects that we consider important, in a funny way and using a lot of irony.

Most of all we want to entertain people and make them laugh their pants off.

If you want to support our channel you can do it at https://www.patreon.com/alwaysfullretard
